      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REDEEM A ARCADIA (2) broke through for his maiden success last time out at this track over 300m (17.77). Looks the testing material. SHE'S SILKY (1) hit the ground running from out wide and on speed early but faded and swamped late when 5th at this track in Grade 4/5 company. Solid record here at the distance winning nine races. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Likely to be thereabouts. BECKY BELLE (4) turned in a plain performance last time when fifth at this track over 300m behind Wow Girl (18.05) in a Grade 5. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Should play a prominent role. DEMENTIA (8) is a course and distance winner who cannot be left out.",
